steps.name: Given The CSV file "CliKintoneTest-24.csv" with content as below:
And Load app ID of the app "app_for_draft_token" as env var: "APP_ID"
And Load app token of the app "app_for_draft_token" with exact permissions "add" as env var: "API_TOKEN"
When I run the command with args "record import --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app $APP_ID --api-token $API_TOKEN --file-path CliKintoneTest-24.csv"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
steps.statusMessage:
AssertionError [ERR_ASSERTION]: [2024-05-22T14:28:45.247Z] INFO: Starting to import records...

steps.name: And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[520] \[GAIA_IA02] The specified API token does not match the API token generated via an app."
